<P><h2 ALIGN=CENTER>Alexey S. SHMAKOV</h2></P>
<img src="shmakov.jpg" alt="Shmakov" BORDER=1 HSPACE="10" ALIGN=LEFT VSPACE="10" align=top>

<B><FONT SIZE=4><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Birth date</B>: November 26, 1982</P>
<B><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Educational background</B>:</P>

<DIR>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">1996-1999 &#8213; Chemico-Biological School ¹ 175, Moscow.<BR>
2000-now &#8213; undergraduate student at the Chair of Entomology, Biological Faculty, Moscow State University.<BR>
</DIR>

<B><P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Scientific interests</B>:</P> 
<DIR>
<P ALIGN=JUSTIFY>Taxonomy and evolution of the order Thysanoptera (Insecta).</DIR>

<B><P>Awards</B>:</P>
<DIR>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">1998 &#8213; Diploma of the International George Soros Science Education Program.<BR>
1998 &#8213;  Secondary Diploma of the Annual All-Russian Olympiad of Geology, Geological Faculty, Moscow State University.<BR>
1999 &#8213; Diploma of All-Russian Ecological Festival, Ministry of Education of Russia.<BR>
</DIR>

<B><P>Expeditions</B>:</P>
<DIR>
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Aug. 2001 &#8213; Expedition of the Paleontological Institute to the Upper Permian-Lower Triassic continental deposits of the Novosibirsk Region, Russia. 
<P ALIGN="JUSTIFY">Aug. 2002 &#8213; Expedition of the Paleontological Institute to the Upper Jurassic continental deposits of the Chita Region, Russia.
</DIR>


<B><P>Publications</B>:</P>
<DIR>
Grimaldi D., Shmakov A., and Fraser N. 2004. Mesozoic thrips and early evolution of the order Thysanoptera (Insecta). <I>Journal of Paleontology</I> <B>78</B> (5): 941–952. [<A HREF="http://apt.allenpress.com/aptonline/?request=get-abstract&issn=0022-3360&volume=078&issue=05&page=0941" TARGET="_BLANK">Abstract</A>]<BR>
Shmakov A.S. 2008. The Jurassic thrips <I>Liassothrips crassipes</I> (Martynov, 1927) and its taxonomic position in the order Thysanoptera (Insecta). <I>Paleontological Journal</I> <B>42</B> (1): 47-52. [<A HREF="http://maik.ru/abstract/paleng/8/paleng1_8p47abs.htm" TARGET="_BLANK">Abstract</A>]&#160;[<A HREF="http://fossilinsects.net/pdfs/Shmakov_2008_PalJ_JurassicLiassothrips_en.pdf" TARGET="_BLANK" TITLE="373K">English PDF</A>]&#160;[<A HREF="http://fossilinsects.net/pdfs/Shmakov_2008_PalJ_JurassicLiassothrips_ruProof.pdf" TARGET="_BLANK" TITLE="368K">Russian PDF</A>]<BR>
